OL,3,CHow to get your kids to listen and
OL,4,Cwant to do what you say
OL,6,FSeven children and a man have died in
OL,7,Fopen water incidents over the Bank
OL,8,FHoliday weekend. So what can parents
OL,9,Fand carers say to help children
OL,10,Funderstand the dangers, and stop them
OL,11,Fwanting to go into the water in the
OL,12,Ffirst place?
OL,14,FDr Charlotte Hilton is a psychologist
OL,15,Fwith expertise in behaviour change and
OL,16,Fcommunication strategies, and shares
OL,17,Fher tips with ITV Central.
OL,19,FNobody likes being told what to do and
OL,20,Fthat includes children and young
OL,21,Fpeople!
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
