PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779894668
OL,3,CHow to get your kids to listen and
OL,4,Cwant to do what you say
OL,6,FThink about the deliberate use of
OL,7,Fclosed questions to confirm something
OL,8,For invite a brief response, and open
OL,9,Fquestions (What, when, where, why,
OL,10,Ftell me, describe and explain), to
OL,11,Finvite detail.
OL,13,FBe intentional in what we ask because
OL,14,Fwe invite what we ask for.
OL,16,F5. Be careful with 'Can you?'
OL,18,FWe say it all the time, 'Can you
OL,19,Fplease help to clear your room?' 'Can
OL,20,Fyou close the door?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
