PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779894668
OL,3,CHow to get your kids to listen and
OL,4,Cwant to do what you say
OL,6,FBut what do we really mean? We
OL,7,Ftypically mean 'Would you please clear
OL,8,Fyour room?' Or 'Would you close that
OL,9,Fdoor please?' But what is often heard
OL,10,Fis 'Are you able to?'
OL,12,FFor people who are neurodivergent and/
OL,13,For think literally, it is especially
OL,14,Fimportant that we pay attention to
OL,15,Fthis because we are simply inviting
OL,16,Fsomeone to respond with 'Yes I can' or
OL,17,F'No I can't.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
