PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779894668
OL,3,CHow to get your kids to listen and
OL,4,Cwant to do what you say
OL,6,FIt's important to remember that there
OL,7,Fis no 'magic wand' when it comes to
OL,8,Fcommunicating with children and young
OL,9,Fpeople but there are strategies that
OL,10,Fhelp to influence the conversation and
OL,11,Foutcomes.
OL,13,FThese strategies are intended to
OL,14,Finfluence the likelihood of children
OL,15,Fmaking choices and behaving in a
OL,16,Fmanner that reflects what you're
OL,17,Fasking of them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
